" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75baeda53a62049190ed199da7e5bda239827bf9","tid":1940093,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3c5d6b2ecd12704701c1b44a18ba5076322246b","tid":1940093,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"現時已知願意攬炒候選人：<br />\n<br />\n新東：<br />\n陳志全 <br />\n<br />\n新西： <br />\n朱凱迪 <br />\n<br />\n大家繼續加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:20:43.000Z","msg":"關於否決財政預算案而逼特首辭職一點<br />\n其實有個細節好似好多人都無去留意<br />\n就係第一次否決後<br />\n立法會會被解散再選<br />\n<br />\n所以要行呢條路首要條件係<br />\n大家有信心重選後都可以35+<br />\n<br />\n所以如果今次過35+係過得好炆<br />\n呢個策略其實幾危險<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得安全D嘅做法係等霸到立法會勞工界三席<br />\n亦即係要等一年，等今年組成嘅工會成爲勞工界選民<br />\n到時再過35+就易好多<br />\n<br />\n講咁多係希望大家<br />\n到時唔好一見議員唔肯否決財政預算案就屌上天<br />\n就算我都認同應該行攬炒呢條路<br />\n如果到時有議員係因爲以上嘅原因，我會明白同理解"},{"pid":"8c121f9603ab5496538520b97198065482d7b7ed","tid":1940093,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d090899f2174d0ce623bf4a201f769065a334c0","tid":1940093,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"唔攬炒唔好選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1009f0b5f00574b96a8a13220e8c959522b181","tid":1940093,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5e2c10c72f057582bcc63e8d4254c5fc9a191e","tid":1940093,"uid":192983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:23:10.000Z","msg":"推(1/10)"},{"pid":"e62990d006c2afd0d2ec1bdcde66bb1c0249c083","tid":1940093,"uid":218447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:23:11.000Z","msg":"一定要承諾攬炒"},{"pid":"9d78d983424165fa822a99acb83d1102cf97873